[{"id": "313eae0e-f8f1-4ea1-87f9-3f20a9c1cb5a", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Setup:\n\nHermione is solo touring europe directly after the war to clear her head. Her and Ron aren't official yet.\n\n\n\nScene: Hermione sitting at a table at an outdoor cafe in france when Victor Krum spots her and comes over to say hello\nASSISTANT: The caf\u00e9 table pressed cool iron slats into the backs of Hermione's thighs through her linen skirt, the fabric already damp from the morning mist off the Seine. Steam curled from her untouched caf\u00e9 au lait, carrying bitter chicory notes that cut through the buttery waft of fresh croissants from the tray beside it. Her copy of *Les Contes de Perrault* lay open, spine cracked at \"La Barbe Bleue,\" but her eyes skimmed without retention\u2014mind looping contingencies: apparition points from Lyon to Vienna, Gringotts exchange rates for French francs, the latest Prophet clippings on Ministry reconstruction folded inside the cover.\n\nFootsteps crunched gravel behind her, heavier than the locals' light shuffle. A shadow eclipsed the page, broad-shouldered against the striped awning.\n\n\"Herm-own-ninny?\"\n\nShe looked up. Viktor Krum loomed there, wool greatcoat slung over one arm despite the July warmth, his nose faintly crooked from old breaks, black hair windswept as if he'd just stepped off a broom. The Quidditch build hadn't softened\u2014shoulders like Bulgarian oak, hands that gripped Bludgers now flexing at his sides.\n\n\"Viktor.\" The name came out precise, volume calibrated before it pitched half an octave higher. Fingers tightened on the book edges, paper crinkling. \"What an unexpected convergence. Are you in Paris for the International Confederation of Wizards' summit? The Prophet mentioned delegations arriving last week.\"\n\nHe pulled out the facing chair without asking, the scrape loud enough to draw a glance from the waiter. Sat with a nod, elbows planting on the tablecloth, gaze steady on her face. \"No summit. Holiday. Training camp end, so... see France. And you? Alone?\"\n\nPosture locked: shoulders squared, chin lifted two degrees. The caf\u00e9 noise blurred\u2014clink of porcelain, murmur of French verbs conjugating around them. \"Solo travel,\" she said, closing the book with a soft thump. \"Post-war decompression. Europe's magical archives are unparalleled for contextualizing reconstruction efforts. The Biblioth\u00e8que des Sorciers here holds first editions on goblin treaties that Hogwarts' restricted section only references in summary.\" Breath steadied. New parameters: polite deflection, no elaboration on Ron's letters left unanswered in her trunk. \"How have you been? Durmstrang must be implementing those anti-dark arts curricula the ICW mandated.\"", "embedding": [-0.019485067576169968, -0.012854639440774918, 0.003467071568593383, 0.006760867778211832, 0.006606653798371553, 0.03676407411694527, 0.06914146989583969, 0.07829274237155914, 0.0019681460689753294, -0.008944161236286163, 0.007833416573703289, -0.042246438562870026, -0.0032078404910862446, -0.022393979132175446, -0.016841469332575798, -0.03963359072804451, 0.0067299725487828255, -0.00019808263459708542, -0.04942987859249115, 0.06413860619068146, -0.05183898285031319, -0.07895708829164505, 0.032756220549345016, 0.03744278848171234, 0.013360817916691303, 0.01693338342010975, -0.060616545379161835, -0.0013631725450977683, -0.0430673323571682, 0.002251710742712021, -0.09477753937244415, 0.02838524803519249, -0.032130371779203415, 0.044866446405649185, 0.0025652700569480658, 0.020731834694743156, 0.06215658783912659, -0.005372396670281887, 0.02940034680068493, 0.013128373771905899, -0.03581392765045166, -0.029986631125211716, -0.13869363069534302, 0.029839329421520233, 0.01609698124229908, 0.024479124695062637, 0.04553872346878052, 0.06397662311792374, -0.048072345554828644, -0.02149050123989582, -0.03319478780031204, 0.03432876616716385, -0.01867000386118889, -0.08072256296873093, -0.10330194979906082, 